{"type": "article", "id": 11912, "title": "马卡龙灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-10T11:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153150ZFHhksxoU1i6QGNm.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙设计师受到法国马卡龙的启发，设计了这一款马卡龙灯具，细心缠绕的线象征马卡龙极需耐心的制作过程，两个木环搭架，中和了缠绕的复杂，使灯具看上去更加简洁。当灯光亮起来，可以透过线材的缝隙洒出来，看起来很是温馨。这款灯具一共有大小不同的两个类型，四种颜色可以选择。<a href=\"http://www.silviacenal.com/#/macaron-lamp/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261358579KFXx3AzvSE8pYuJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135858sBj4gpGaDOc56K9Y.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"636\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135858cnWbBRODwZIdoGL0.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613585932FXNBfcwYt0nvMK.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135859xyRrsqtiDBMegbnI.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"894\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}